      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Offered for sale is a mint-condition example that presents exceptionally well and has clearly been very well cared for. The paint, interior, and overall finish show minimal wear, and it stands out as a clean, sharp vehicle that is ready to enjoy immediately. This is the kind of car that will appeal to buyers looking for a truly well-kept example rather than a project or average driver.",
