    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable, practical, and priced to move, this vehicle is a smart choice for buyers seeking dependable basic transportation without a big upfront cost. It shows honest wear consistent with age and use, but offers solid value for anyone needing an inexpensive daily driver, backup vehicle, or starter car. A straightforward opportunity to get behind the wheel at a very accessible price.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap runabout with character? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest little machine that could be a great fit for someone needing affordable transport, a project, or a practical spare. It\u2019s priced fairly for what it is, and with a bit of care from the next owner, there\u2019s still plenty of life and usefulness to enjoy. If you want something straightforward, budget-friendly, and ready to go to its next home, come have a look.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver with strong mechanical fundamentals and plenty of life left for the right owner. Engine starts up willingly, pulls cleanly through the rev range, and the transmission does its job as it should. Not a show car, but a usable platform with honest wear, dependable road manners, and clear value for someone who wants affordable transportation or a project with good bones. Recent maintenance attention helps it feel more sorted than most in this category. Priced to move and worth a look if you know how to spot a practical buy.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap entry car with honest wear. Not pretty, still gets the job done. Priced to move fast.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Here\u2019s a car with stories in its steel and plenty of road still ahead. It has that hard-to-fake, lived-in character that makes an older vehicle feel approachable, useful, and real\u2014perfect for someone who wants affordable wheels with personality instead of just another anonymous commuter. Whether you need a practical around-town driver, a second vehicle, or a project with promise, this one offers a chance to get behind the wheel without stretching the budget. A straightforward, no-pretense ride with honest charm and room for its next chapter.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next owner, this vehicle offers straightforward transportation at an approachable price. An excellent fit for buyers seeking an inexpensive daily driver or a solid starting point for a project, it delivers strong value for the money. Priced to sell and worth a closer look.",
      "price": 4995.0,
