      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Honest little car that\u2019s priced to move and could be a great fit for someone looking for an affordable runaround or a project. It\u2019s not perfect, but it\u2019s a straightforward, budget-friendly option with plenty of usable life for the right buyer. If you\u2019re handy with cars or just need something inexpensive without the fancy price tag, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Solid project or budget driver with a strong-running powertrain, responsive automatic transmission, and well-sorted road manners. The engine pulls cleanly, steering feels direct, and the chassis remains composed, making it an easy candidate for daily use, light restoration, or a dependable spare vehicle. Shows its age cosmetically and will benefit from continued TLC, but it presents as an honest, serviceable car with good bones and plenty of life left for the next owner. Priced to move for someone who appreciates mechanical potential over showroom perfection.",
